msgstr "行为准则"

#: ../../development/contributing.md:86 f0da427d576a43f59d25050e3aa89aed
msgid ""
"Please be respectful and constructive in all interactions. We aim to "
"create a welcoming and inclusive community."
msgstr "请在所有互动中保持尊重和建设性。我们致力于创建一个友好和包容的社区。"

#: ../../development/contributing.md:88 d22a4c47e83c40b5b68d3e96fa771f87
msgid "Reporting Issues"
msgstr "报告问题"

#: ../../development/contributing.md:90 e9bf47fa3e2f43e18771dc0444ccf697
msgid ""
"Use [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/zjowowen/notebooklm/issues) to "
"report bugs or request features (when enabled)"
msgstr ""
"使用 [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/zjowowen/notebooklm/issues) "
"报告错误或请求功能（启用后可用）"

#: ../../development/contributing.md:91 e633e59a00b6442ca5036ad4921161d2
msgid "Include clear steps to reproduce any bugs"
msgstr "包含清晰的错误复现步骤"

#: ../../development/contributing.md:92 a314a95cd156486b8fabcaf0c6dca631
msgid "Provide environment details (OS, Node.js version, browser)"
msgstr "提供环境详情（操作系统、Node.js 版本、浏览器）"
